---------------------------------------------------------------------------
Use Hibernate directly vs. via JPA
---------------------------------------------------------------------------

1.) Use Hibernate

    Spring app ---> Hibernate

2.) Use JPA with Hibernate as implementation

    Spring app ---> JPA <-impl- Hibernate (or EclipseLinkk, OpenJPA, ...)



---------------------------------------------------------------------------
Differences
---------------------------------------------------------------------------

	            | Hibernate	        | JPA
-----------------------------------------------------------
Core concept	| Session	        | EntityManager
Created by	    | SessionFactory    | EntityManagerFactory
Entities are    | Session	        | Persistence context
stored inâ€¦	    |                   |
Query language	| HQL	            | JPQL
-----------------------------------------------------------